    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Show AdMob and iAd banner class (Mediation support)]]></title>
    <link href="http://lab.dolice.net/blog/2013/09/04/objc-classes-dc-banner-en/"/>
    <updated>2013-09-04T22:35:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://lab.dolice.net/blog/2013/09/04/objc-classes-dc-banner-en</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/images/article/dc-banner-screenshot.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>I created to display the switching of advertising iAd and AdMob the "<a href="http://gum.co/dc-app-purchase-en" title="DCBanner">DCBanner</a>" class. I am using this class in the app was released.</p>

<p>I have sold at 99¢ and sample source code, documentation in Gumroad.</p>

<h2>Download</h2>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://gum.co/dc-banner2-en">http://gum.co/dc-banner2-en</a></li>
</ul>


<h2>How to display the banner</h2>

<p>Can be done with one line display of the banner. To read the "DCBanner.h" file, specify as follows in viewDidAppear method.</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="p">[[</span><span class="n">DCBanner</span> <span class="n">sharedManager</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="nl">showAdBanner:</span><span class="n">self</span> <span class="nl">yPos:</span><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">view</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">frame</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">size</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">height</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">50</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h2>How to remove a banner</h2>

<p>You can remove the banner is specified as follows.</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="p">[[</span><span class="n">DCBanner</span> <span class="n">sharedManager</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="n">removeAdBanner</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h2>Installation procedure</h2>

<h3>1. Add SDK</h3>

<p>Expand the Downloaded file, and then add it to the project folder Ad.</p>

<h3>2. Add necessary framework</h3>

<p>Framework of seven following so you will need, I will read each.</p>

<ol>
<li>Security.framework</li>
<li>iAd.framework</li>
<li>AdSupport.framework</li>
<li>SystemConfiguration.framework</li>
<li>MessageUI.framework</li>
<li>AudioToolbox.framework</li>
<li>StoreKit.framework</li>
</ol>


<h3>3. Edit Build Settings</h3>

<p><img src="/images/article/dc-banner_en.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>Open "TARGETS" → "Build Settings", and then described as "<em>-ObjC </em>" in the field of [Other Linker Flags] of [Linking].</p>

<h3>4. Add to DCBanner.h the AdMob unit ID</h3>

<p>Open the DCBanner.h file, specify the ID of the ad unit AdMob in the line 12 to "GAD_UNIT_ID".</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">h1</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">define</span> <span class="n">GAD_UNIT_ID</span> <span class="s">@&quot;ca-app-pub-0667784050147760/9058240228&quot;</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">h1</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
]]></content>
